{"tid":2497552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來柴狗咬死貓既貓主 只係一個小妹妹","createTime":"2021-04-20T15:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T15:24:26.000Z","uid":42246,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2ebbadffd1039a65e5271f992b8bd5e1f4d6253","tid":2497552,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9fN0Yo5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9fN0Yo5.png&h=797b93ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「香港寵物節2021」日前在灣仔會展舉行，在展期最後一日（4月18日）卻發生悲劇，一隻柴犬涉嫌當場咬死5星期大的小貓「卷卷」。貓主Gloria指，因年紀尚小的卷卷要定時食奶，她又要在展會上班，故才帶同貓貓開工。對於突然痛失愛貓，Gloria哭訴，「如果我早知會咁，我就算要請假無埋份工，都唔會帶佢去」，在訪問字裡行間，她亦揭開卷卷的悲慘身世。<br />\n<br />\n貓主Gloria接受《香港01》訪問時表示，自己好鍾意動物，曾擔任獸醫護士7至8年，一直都全力幫忙拯救浪浪，以前亦會與醫生義診，醫流浪牛及貓狗，家中亦養有兩隻貓及兩隻兔。大半個月前，她幫義工暫託3星期大的流浪貓卷卷，牠性格乖巧，非常親人，深受一家人寵愛。►毛孩子有IG了，來追蹤我們吧！<br />\n<br />\n相處半個月視如己出<br />\n<br />\n「貓b到家時體重只有200g，好瘦，我湊到佢肥嘟嘟，牠5個星期大，已經有一磅多。」Gloria指，早前她另一隻19歲的金毛尋回犬離世，火化之後隔日，她就接了卷卷回家，不期然將對狗狗的感情，投放落卷卷身上。「卷卷日日黏住晒，連瞓覺都要在我身上瞓」。<br />\n<br />\n因卷卷年紀尚小，要每兩小時食一次奶，故Gloria日前唯有帶同卷卷到寵物節上班，豈料最後卻發生柴犬涉嫌當場咬死卷卷的悲慘一事。Gloria對此後悔不已，「如果我早知會咁，我就算要請假無埋份工，都唔會帶佢去」，同時她亦道出卷卷的悲慘身世......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGloria表示，因為是次事件未完結，警方仍在調查中，所以卷卷的遺體現時只能雪藏在善終公司的雪櫃，不能夠火化，「我希望快點為卷卷討回公道，之後火化牠，將牠帶回家」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來只係個小妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班怪貓主撚真係冇人性過支那人<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母咁撚冇性真係拎來喂柴犬岩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec451a887d5c77028ac2c834983b1305156710e","tid":2497552,"uid":148017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"牠只是個孩子啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f99c6cb6abeae4d7b5a0e9770213cb29f54d11","tid":2497552,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"接受香港01訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58490b80123eb3ab45e31e44653d7adeec978f8d","tid":2497552,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:06:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088ce8e16b5dee8935eb094c9e83efedb8806bcc","tid":2497552,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d5f99c6cb6abeae4d7b5a0e9770213cb29f54d11","tid":2497552,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"接受香港01訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"hk01  主動騷擾小妹妹 小妹妹唔識處理"},{"pid":"c5cc0c729d843a85e46023dce0d387b761aa4cbb","tid":2497552,"uid":71657,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:07:24.000Z","msg":"做咗獸醫護士7-8年都仲小妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以一出世就開始做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9b40bfcbd6f2993c536dd952842424a23b49fe","tid":2497552,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"邊個再怪貓主 就係支那人隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffa0c08bcda4e4f6886fb1bb4d3fa50ae66e244","tid":2497552,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5cc0c729d843a85e46023dce0d387b761aa4cbb","tid":24